<ab facs="#facs_447_r2l5"><expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> daran geweıſt / . daʒ er <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> klag auf </ab>
