<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Sawnsheim <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>S<ex>eicz</ex></expan>
<expan>Gewd<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> daran geweist, daz er
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> klag auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> lantgericht
                                <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wil, also daz im ewr gnade
                                <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und pfingsten tag bescheide und
                        des <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> helffe; daran er sich vor
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Conrad <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Sawnsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>
<expan>benüge<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen wil, also ob der czü im iht
                        czesprechen hab, daz er sich daran von <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bey uns czü
                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> benügen lazz, do er im des
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein wölle. Und wo wir ew etc. </ab>
</div>
